data.description: Terrific East Cobb home in a quiet cul-de-sac community of only 27 homes. Updated in 2018. Hardwood floors throughout - No carpet. Great  split-lvl open floor plan. Large vaulted Great Rm w/stone FPLC. Separate Dining Rm. Bright eat-in  updated Kitchen w/white cabinets, lg island, abundant cabinets, modern SS appliances and more. Spacious, vaulted Master BR w/walk-in closet. Updated Master Bath w/dbl vanities, jetted tub and oversized shwr. Two more good sized BRs, another Full Bath and a Laundry closet complete the bedroom level. On the Terrace lvl there is a 2nd Family Rm, 4th BR and another Full Bath plus access to the very oversized 2-car garage. In the back is a lg deck overlooking private woods and an extended deck area within the woods as well. Nearby swim / tennis options, abundant shops / restaurants and easy hwy access complete this great home.
